Four people including a KDF officer have been arrested in connection with kidnapping a 24 year old in Kasarani. Without naming names, DCI director George Kinoti said the 24 year old man was kidnapped in his residence at Kasarani and taken to unknown place. Upon receiving this report from the victims relative, investigations commenced immediately leading to the rescue of the victim who was holed up in a house at Kahawa Wendani where the four individuals, two men and two women were found therein. A Toyota Noah that was used to pick the victim from his house, the victim's mobile phone among other items were recovered. The four are in custody as further investigations take place.